# Marketplace Pipeline — Core Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` before non-trivial changes.

## Stack

Python 3.11 · Pydantic v2 · httpx · tenacity · FastAPI · uvicorn · pytest · ruff

## Entry points

| Command | Interface |
|---------|-----------|
| `marketplace-pipeline` | CLI — sync one-shot run |
| `marketplace-pipeline-api` | FastAPI — async jobs on :8000 |
| `marketplace-pipeline-worker` | Celery worker (scale profile) |
| `make run` / `make api` | Mock smoke for CLI / API |
| `make scale-up` | Docker compose scale profile |

## Business invariants

- Partial collection (< target) is success when category exhausted
- Parser errors → graceful degradation, never crash on partial data
- CRM idempotency: SHA-256(title+description), store at `data/crm_idempotency.json`
- `MOCK_PARSER` is env-only (no separate mock HTTP server)
- Segment «Стандарт» classified but not sent to CRM
- API jobs: request `collection_target` overrides settings for that job

## Code style

- External HTTP only through `HttpClient` (shared pool, close via context manager or Container)
- Settings via `infrastructure/config/settings.py`, never raw `os.environ` in modules
- New domain models in `domain/`; API schemas in `interfaces/api/schemas/`
- Line length 100, ruff clean

## Before commit

```bash
ruff check src tests && pytest
```

Coverage must stay ≥95%.
